dia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"for ad-free news and current affairs  Olympics 2024 RSS  Follow RNZ News\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3066, \"end\": 3069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 0.9909084061258754, \"rank\": 0.009173927374278374, \"text\": \"RSS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}, {\"begin\": 3078, \"end\": 3081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RNZ\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}]}"